<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3534750>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Megophrys shunhuangensis sp. nov. holotype: adult male (HNNU16SH02: SVL 33.6 mm) in life: A. dorsal view; B. ventral view; E. lateral view showing dark wide stripe in the forearm; F. ventral view of hand; G. ventral view of foot. Paratype: adult female (HNNU16SH04: SVL 37.6 mm) in life C. dorsal view; D. ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3534750/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3534752>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Megophrys shunhuangensis sp. nov. holotype: adult male (HNNU16SH02: SVL 33.6 mm) in preservation: A. dorsal view; B. ventral view; E. ventral view of hand; F. ventral view of foot; G. nuptial pads on the first and second fingers; H. profile view of head; I. discontinuous linear line on the posterior edge of the tongue. Paratype: adult female (HNNU16SH04: SVL 37.6 mm) in preservation C. dorsal view; D. ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3534752/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3534754>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Habitats of M. shunhuangensis sp. nov. in the type locality, a small stream at the edge of Shunhuang Mountain." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3534754/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3534756>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Habitats of M. shunhuangensis sp. nov. in the type locality, a small-clearance washed by mountain streams." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3534756/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3534746>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Bayesian inference tree derived from partial DNA sequences of the mitochondrial 12S rRNA + 16S rRNA gene. Numbers after slashes are bootstrap support for maximum likelihood (1000 replicates) analyses (>50 retained) and numbers before slash indicate Bayesian posterior probabilities (>0.50 retained). The symbol “-” represents bootstrap value below 50." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3534746/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

